not_summary.tsv` via `write.table(..., sep='\\t', row.names=F,\ncol.names=T, quote=F)`. Do not emit any PDF plot.\n\n## Deliverables\n\n- At least `output/homer_annot_summary.tsv` must exist when you submit.\n- Full output set expected: homer_annot_summary.tsv under `output/`.\n\nWhen the deliverables are in `output/`, call `submit_done(success=true)` with a short\nsummary of how you solved it.\n\n## Workspace (read-only summary)\n```json\n{\n  \"OBJECTIVE.md\": {\n    \"_file\": \"OBJECTIVE.md\"\n  },\n  \"input\": {\n    \"sampleA_annot.txt\": {\n      \"_file\": \"sampleA_annot.txt\"\n    },\n    \"sampleB_annot.txt\": {\n      \"_file\": \"sampleB_annot.txt\"\n    },\n    \"sampleC_annot.txt\": {\n      \"_file\": \"sampleC_annot.txt\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"meta.json\": {\n    \"_file\": \"meta.json\"\n  },\n  \"output\": {}\n}\n```\n\nSuccess hint: when `output/homer_annot_summary.tsv` exists under the workspace, you may call submit_done(success=true).\n"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_rKafBzGUYbsysdLSjK4fJo3G", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"plan\": \"1. Read the HOMER annotatePeaks output files: sampleA_annot.txt, sampleB_annot.txt, and sampleC_annot.txt.\\n2. For each file, extract the 'Annotation' column and aggregate feature counts by the first whitespace token.\\n3. Cast the aggregated data into a wide matrix format with samples as rows and features as columns.\\n4. Save the resulting matrix to output/homer_annot_summary.tsv using write.table with specified parameters.\\n5. Verify the existence of the output file and submit the task as complete.\"}", "name": "write_plan"}}]}, {"role": "tool", "content": "Wrote plan (500 chars) to .plan.md", "name": "write_plan", "tool_call_id": "call_rKafBzGUYbsysdLSjK4fJo3G"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_GP5PvrbX5E6N9klrmJKXjFzt", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"relat